{"tid":2257962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拜山祭祖拜撚到連自己祖先個墳都燒撚埋，到底華人文化係唔係真係戇鳩既合集？","createTime":"2020-10-25T15:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T08:05:11.000Z","uid":309192,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a80c4141f75613757a4113e069d3f30532c3b3a","tid":2257962,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"燒撚完D樹都唔知要幾多十年先生得番哂出黎<br />\n又唔知燒撚死幾多動物同昆蟲<br />\n燒成咁D毒煙又會影響好多民居<br />\n仲未計要救火既消防員都好危險<br />\n<br />\n到時佢地拜先人就分分鐘產生更加多先人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下年拜撚完又燒過又產生更多先人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底燒撚到咁佢地既祖先會安寧嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜你老母呀拜 戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htpJibd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtpJibd.jpg&h=8b1cdb93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f789cfc2f81f4a3e4002f44f2857a0184776f3d2","tid":2257962,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a970b5b23d35aaf8ddba923d2ad3c8e3ec1781df","tid":2257962,"uid":366245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"218de79b4d6bbd5e01022bfd799e94e93d89c548","tid":2257962,"uid":54901,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:26:05.000Z","msg":"啲人真係仆街冚家剷"},{"pid":"13c5933ddc0cb4470ae735c625a49